-- Malaysia's CIMB, RHB shares halted ahead of "material announcement"
-- By Yantoultra Ngui
-- Tue Oct 21, 2014 03:07AM EDT
-- None



KUALA LUMPUR, Oct 21 (Reuters) - Malaysia's CIMB Group Holdings Bhd <CIMB.KL> and RHB Capital Bhd <RHBC.KL>, the country's second and fourth largest lenders respectively, said on Tuesday afternoon that their shares will be suspended from trading in afternoon trade pending the release of a material announcement.

Loan provider Malaysia Building Society Bhd <MBSS.KL> also said its shares will be suspended on the same day.